# Vision theme – build after style changes

When you edit Vision theme styles (SCSS or CSS under `wp-content/themes/vision/`), **run the theme build** so changes are compiled and reflected:

```bash
cd wp-content/themes/vision && npm run build
```

- SCSS is in `src/scss/` and compiles to `style.css` (and `assets/css/main.css` when using build:css).
- Always run `npm run build` (or `npm run build:css`) after changing any `.scss` or theme CSS.
